name: Roads to Oblivion - Lower Left
description:
1 of 5 sections from the original piece. Visual Imagery of deciding which road to take. A question many of us ask at various crossroads in our lives. Sometimes, ALL roads seem to go nowhere.... and this is when we need to take a deep breath and forge forward into the unknown. Trust our natural instincts and see where the path takes us!
